{"id":211344,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/中国媒体删节林书豪访谈/","date":"2012-02-19T23:39:36Z","modified":"2012-02-19T23:39:36Z","title":"中国媒体删节林书豪访谈","content":"<p>占领青少年思想阵地 写道 &#8220;最近备受媒体关注的美国华裔NBA球星林书豪是一位虔诚的基督徒，他表示自己打篮球是为了神的荣耀。林书豪自述在遭遇挫折时会想到圣经里苦难磨练品格的章节，在神的引导下重新开始，并称自己打进NBA就可以利用全国电视转播和媒体来宣扬他的信仰，来讲神在他的生命中为他做了多少。不过很多中国球迷可能不知道上帝对林书豪篮球事业的意义：一位网友发现包括新华网在内的中国媒体在转述林书豪及其母亲的访谈内容时，都精心删除了提到上帝和信仰的段落。&#8221;<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1cc1d7ff/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&#038;title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E5%88%A0%E8%8A%82%E6%9E%97%E4%B9%A6%E8%B1%AA%E8%AE%BF%E8%B0%88&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsolidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F02%2F19%2F0327234%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E5%88%A0%E8%8A%82%E6%9E%97%E4%B9%A6%E8%B1%AA%E8%AE%BF%E8%B0%88&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsolidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F02%2F19%2F0327234%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/126178423461/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1cc1d7ff/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/126178423461/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1cc1d7ff/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/126178423461/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1cc1d7ff/a2t.img\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=KFXaN9qxsh0:gd1MQL8LK5g:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=KFXaN9qxsh0:gd1